"""Test get_device_group_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_device_group_stats(device_group_id=self.p_data.
    device_group_id, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now, end_time=
    self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.DEV_GRP))
